Our team is switching to using Choreo’s AutoRoutines this year in order to have greater flexibility and control over our autonomous routines. When using Choreo’s native AutoChooser, however, a string shows up in Elastic instead of the expected sendableChooser. Has anyone else ran into this problem? If so, what was your solution? We use command-based robot code.
